high_descs: Turn around, hang a left at the wall and walk to the white fridge across the room.
Open the upper door, pick up the white plate from the top shelf and close the door.
Turn left, hang a left around the counter and walk to the stove on your right.
Place the plate in the microwave above the stove, heat for three seconds, remove the plate and close the door.
Turn right, hang a right at the counter and walk to the fridge on your left.
Open the bottom door, plate the plate on the middle shelf to the right of the tomato, and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate in a fridge.

high_descs: turn around and head forward then turn left and the wall and walk to the fridge across the room
Open the fridge and pick up the plate that is on the top shelf of the freezer then close the fridge
Turn left and head to the stove
Open the microwave above the stove and place the plate inside and close the door and turn it on. Then open the microwave and take out the place and close the door
Turn around and head to the fridge across the room to your left
Open the fridge and place the plate on the middle shelf to the right of the tomato
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate into a fridge

high_descs: Walk to the fridge on your right.
Take the plate out of the freezer.
Turn left and go to the microwave over the stove.
Heat the plate and hold it again.
Turn right and go back to the fridge.
Put the plate in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed plate in the fridge.
